[[File:Wall_tower_ranger.png|right]]The '''Ranger Tower''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It increases the Defensive Value of a limited number of Rangers by 100%. If there are not enough Rangers in the city, City Guards can take their place and gain the same bonus. These towers don't count towards a city's building number limit.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 3

